Interface RequestGuardFactory<T extends RequestGuard>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the RequestGuard type that this factory produces.
    All Known Subinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface RequestGuardFactory<T extends RequestGuard>
    Factory for constructing RequestGuard instances from HTTP requests. See RequestGuard for details about this API.

    • Method Summary

    • Method Detail

      • newInstance

        T newInstance(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> pathParams,
              java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> queryParams,
              Request request,
              TypeAdapterFactory factory)
        Provide a RequestGuard instance based on the request information. The logic of implementations of this method should be used to provide prerequisites
        Parameters:
        pathParams - the raw named path parameter bindings
        queryParams - the raw named query parameter bindings
        request - the Request representing this request
        factory - the top level TypeAdapterFactory for the application
        Returns:
        a new instance of the RequestGuard produced by this factory. Error cases can return null in error cases. This API is subject to change.
